<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.6">
<l>tēraṇaṅ kalkul ceḻuṅkayal kaṇṇi</l>
<l>tiṟattoru maṟattoḻil purintu</l>
<l>pāraṇaṅ kimilē ṟēḻumuṉ ṉaṭartta</l>
<l>paṉimukil vaṇṇaṉem perumāṉ</l>
<l>kāraṇan taṉṉāl kaṭumpuṉal kayatta</l>
<l>karuvarai piḷaveḻak kutti</l>
<l>vāraṇaṅ koṇarnta kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our great lord, the one the color of misty clouds, who once controlled</l>
<l rend="indent">seven humped bulls that afflicted the world,</l>
<l>Performing a brave deed for the sake of the one with chariot-shaped hips</l>
<l rend="indent">and plump kāyal [-fish] eyes,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges</l>
<l rend="indent">which carried [away] elephants,</l>
<l>Having pounded so that gaps appeared in the dark mountains</l>
<l rend="indent">where hurtling waters spewed for that reason.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
